Package com.canabang.genietext.transit.model.processor.dbase

Class Summary
Bus The Bus class represents a bus in the transit system.
Direction A direction that a bus goes to.
DottedIntersection A location represented using the dotted notation (ie: Walkley.Jasper means the intersection of Walkey street and Jasper street).
Intersection A location.
Schedule The schedule associated with a bus in the transit service.
SlashedIntersection A location represented using the slash notation (ie: Walkley/Jasper or Walkley\Jasper means the intersection of Walkey street and Jasper street).
Station The station or stop number associated with a bus.
TransitService A simulator for a transit service database.
TransitTime Represents a time in the transit service.
TransitTimeComparator Allows transit times to be compared to see which one is greater, smaller, or equal to another.
